              "id": "4f175677",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<h2><strong>Commercial Carpet Cleaning That Protects Your Brand Image and Investment</strong></h2><p>Your carpets work hard for your business. From high-traffic hallways to busy reception areas, they face daily wear that affects appearance and the health and safety of your workplace.</p><p>At Midland Floor Care, we provide specialized commercial carpet cleaning that keeps your floors looking professional, extends their lifespan, and improves the environment for employees, clients, and visitors.</p><p><strong>Why professional carpet cleaning is essential for businesses</strong></p><ul><li><p>First impressions matter: clean, fresh carpets reinforce your professional image</p></li><li><p>Long-term cost savings: regular deep cleaning extends carpet life and reduces replacements</p></li><li><p>Healthier indoor air: removes dust, allergens, and bacteria trapped in fibers</p></li><li><p>Minimal downtime: fast-drying methods keep operations moving</p></li></ul><p>\u00a0</p><p><strong>Our commercial carpet cleaning process</strong></p><ol><li><p>On-site assessment: identify high-traffic zones, stains, and problem areas</p></li><li><p>Pre-treatment: targeted solutions loosen embedded dirt and stains</p></li><li><p>Hot water extraction: industry-grade steam cleaning removes deep contaminants</p></li><li><p>Spot and stain removal: focused treatment for a uniform appearance</p></li><li><p>Carpet grooming: fibers are reset for faster drying and a professional finish</p></li></ol><p>\u00a0</p><p><strong>Industries we serve</strong></p><ul><li><p>Corporate offices</p></li><li><p>Retail and shopping centers</p></li><li><p>Hotels and hospitality</p></li><li><p>Healthcare facilities</p></li><li><p>Schools and universities</p></li><li><p>Government and municipal buildings</p></li></ul><p>\u00a0</p><p><strong>Why businesses choose Midland Floor Care</strong></p><ul><li><p>Experienced commercial specialists for high-traffic environments</p></li><li><p>Commercial-grade equipment for deeper, longer-lasting results</p></li><li><p>Flexible scheduling: after-hours and weekends available</p></li><li><p>Satisfaction guaranteed: backed by our Midland Shine Standard</p></li></ul><p>\u00a0</p><p><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\"><strong>Ready to schedule an on-site visit?</strong></a><br />Call us or request a visit online and we\u2019ll build a plan around your facility.</p><p>Thank you,<br />Justin Campbell</p><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/floor-care-services/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Services</a><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Home</a><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/7-essential-tips-for-impeccable-commercial-floor-care-services/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">7 Essential Tips for Impeccable Commercial Floor Care Services</a><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Schedule Your Visit &amp; Quote</a><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/covid19-protected-services/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">COVID19 Protected</a>",
                "align": "left",
                "text_color": "#0F1411",
